<overview>
<p>This query finds local variables that shadow like-named field declarations. This is confusing since it might easily lead to assignments 
to the local variable that should have been to the corresponding field.</p>

</overview>
<section title="How to Address the Query Results">
<p>For clarity, it may be better to rename the variable to avoid shadowing.</p>



</section>
